metadata.name: # 1  NATASHA / PURPLE
metadata.description:
First lady.

we had a very spontaneous meeting with her, we were subscribed to each other and I liked the atmosphere of her Instagram account, but we didn't know each other personally.

but one day she came into the coffee shop with her family where I worked.

they left me a tip and I was very pleased, her face seemed familiar to me and I decided to ask on instagram if it was her, she said yes)

we exchanged compliments and texted and agreed on a shoot.

the day we met, I was silent at first, as I always am with new acquaintances.

our route was to a small wooden house outside of town, we hailed a cab and hit the road. 

on the way to the house we stopped at a grocery store and Natasha bought some food:

(sausages, a loaf of black bread and beans, since then I liked beans and eat them with pleasure, besides, they are nutritious)

as I recall, it was august, but maybe I'm wrong.

to my senses, to my recollection, it was like this.

continued in the next 1/1 NFT...
